00:00:00.180 --> 00:00:02.940
- This is the world's
largest earthquake simulator.

00:00:02.940 --> 00:00:05.280
It's called E-Defense.

00:00:05.280 --> 00:00:09.540
Its huge shake table can
support a 10-story building

00:00:09.540 --> 00:00:11.670
and then move it in all directions

00:00:11.670 --> 00:00:15.123
with the force of the world's
most destructive earthquakes.

00:00:16.590 --> 00:00:19.290
E-Defense has conducted
more than a hundred tests,

00:00:19.290 --> 00:00:21.630
subjecting all kinds of buildings

00:00:21.630 --> 00:00:24.360
to different simulated earthquakes,

00:00:24.360 --> 00:00:26.220
all to learn how to make buildings

00:00:26.220 --> 00:00:27.693
more earthquake-resistant.

